Azure Resource Locks prevent accidental deletion or modification of critical resources.

Types:

* Delete lock
* Read-only lock

For example, a production database can be protected from accidental deletion.

# Real-Life Use Case:
A real-life use case is safeguarding mission-critical infrastructure.

# Real-Life Example:
Another example is preventing junior admins from modifying sensitive production systems.

Resource locks act as an operational safeguard.
